Class Position

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.coronabounce.models.Position
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable
    public class Position
extends Object
implements Cloneable
    Class used to save coordinates of person.
    Position are always between x & y limits of the controller.
